commitMessage:
[Breaking] Remove support for MacOS 13 on x86_64 (#1732)

This is slowing down CI too much. This change also increases some of the
Ubuntu runner corecounts to improve CI runtime.
Add implementation for Google Cloud Storage with REST (#1645)

Fix formatting in configuration-intro (#1742)

Restrict replacing curly brackets in the `md` to `mdx` conversion to
comments in `js` codeblocks.
